In a Next.js + Vercel setup, there was a case where access from within the EU region needed to be blocked due to GDPR compliance. This was implemented using Middleware, and the following is a memo of the process:

1. Create a page to be displayed when blocked at src/app/geoblocked/page.tsx, where the page to be shown when blocked is created.
```jsx
import type { Metadata } from "next";
export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: "Access blocked",
};
export default ...
```
